1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,500
A website does not have to be broken to fail you.
It can work exactly as its owner designed it.

2
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:15,300
And still omit the feature your life depends on.
OpenPatch is a public feature layer for websites users do not control.

3
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:23,800
MetroCare is a credible twelve-provider directory.
But there is no search, combined filtering, or comparison.

4
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:32,100
To find wheelchair access, Urdu, and new patients,
you must inspect every card yourself.

5
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:38,500
OpenPatch creates a privacy-safe Repair Brief
with bounded structural signals for Codex.

6
00:00:38,500 --> 00:00:44,800
Field values, cookies, storage, query strings,
and page text never enter the brief.

7
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:54,500
GPT-5.6 through Codex inspects the DOM and screenshots,
defines acceptance criteria, and chooses constrained operations.

8
00:00:54,500 --> 00:01:04,600
It cannot provide JavaScript, HTML, callbacks, fetches,
cookies, templates, or arbitrary page-text extraction.

9
00:01:04,600 --> 00:01:11,800
Now the exact constrained runtime is active.
Eleven of eleven operations are healthy.

10
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:19,200
Two providers become a keyboard-accessible comparison table
built only from declared data attributes.

11
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:28,000
Wheelchair access, Urdu, and accepting new patients
reduce twelve services to one understandable choice.

12
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:36,800
Preferences stay local, results are announced,
and our browser test proves the interactions emit zero requests.

13
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:45,800
The extension discovers the community feature automatically
and shows scope, permissions, integrity, and compatibility.

14
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:54,700
One click installs it. Everyone downstream needs
no AI, account, or API key.

15
00:01:54,700 --> 00:02:01,300
The Compatibility Sentinel checks every published target
in Chromium every six hours.

16
00:02:01,300 --> 00:02:07,800
If the original site changes, the patch is quarantined
before another user discovers it.

17
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:17,000
Built in this primary GPT-5.6 and Codex thread:
40 unit tests, 14 browser journeys, and 4 extension tests.

18
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:26,100
When a site will not add the feature people need, users still can.
Fix the web you have.
